### HELLO
grantmd.github.com is Myles Grant. I like to [contribute to Flamework](https://github.com/grantmd/flamework), [maintain my own fork for my quadcopter](https://github.com/grantmd/AeroQuad), [tinker with embedded/RTOS programming](https://github.com/grantmd/ChibiCopter), and [experiment with webgl](https://github.com/grantmd/three.js-experiments).
